close_reason: Merged via PR #18
body: "On 2026-05-27 the daily release publish step in this repo plus all 18 peer pm-* repos failed with E404 even though provenance signing succeeded. The repo was tagged + committed at the new version but npm rejected the PUT. Replace the publish step with a resilient version: skip when version is already on npm, retry the provenance publish up to 3 times with 30s sleep, then fall back to a non-provenance publish."
